===Etymology===
From Germanic ''*surgō''.  Cognate with Old Saxon [[sorga]] (Dutch [[zorg]]), Old High German [[sorga]] (German [[Sorge]]), Old Norse [[sorg]] (Swedish [[sorg#Swedish|sorg]]), Gothic [[𐍃𐌰𐌿𐍂𐌲𐌰]].

